WEBVTT

00:07:28.280 --> 00:07:31.176
Could bringing fonio
to the rest of the world

00:07:31.200 --> 00:07:32.400
be the answer?

00:07:34.520 --> 00:07:36.656
Ancient grains are getting more popular,

00:07:36.680 --> 00:07:41.456
and sales of gluten-free items
are growing in the US --

00:07:41.480 --> 00:07:44.696
16.4 percent since 2013,

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:48.880
making it a 23.3-billion-dollar industry.

00:07:50.960 --> 00:07:53.440
How could fonio
partake in this market share?

00:07:55.960 --> 00:07:58.520
There are many challenges
in turning fonio into food.

00:07:59.360 --> 00:08:02.816
Traditional processing
is laborious and time-consuming,